%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ho%C3%A0ng/T%E1%BA%B7ng-L%C3%BD-Trung-Hoa/poem-B3B4ONq3PvjnkyJbXW05CQ">Tặng Lý Trung Hoa - 贈李中華</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ho%C3%A0ng/author-Bv_13JyNN8dkEbpigVAFGg">Lương Hoàng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/Th%E1%BA%A5t-nguy%E1%BB%87t-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-c%E1%BB%ADu-nh%E1%BA%ADt-S%C3%B9ng-Nh%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-y%E1%BA%BFn-t%C3%A1c/poem-XvdD3URRq0h3cv5mMsfAEw">Thất nguyệt nhị thập cửu nhật Sùng Nhượng trạch yến tác - 七月二十九日崇讓宅宴作</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thương Ẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Thu-t%E1%BB%A9-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-xg4Q2f9EJAHrzl5Hg0bYhA">Thu tứ kỳ 3 - 秋思其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%C4%A9nh/T%E1%BB%91ng-h%E1%BB%AFu-chi-L%C4%A9nh-Nam/poem-xX9zZpyfISo_oDaQAcUoeA">Tống hữu chi Lĩnh Nam - 送友之嶺南</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-D%C4%A9nh/author-FLeQSz8PiNWt7aZh3N_djw">Lý Dĩnh</a>)<br></div>	</div>
